Class GraphImplementation<I,N,D>

    I -

    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Graph<I,N,D>

    public class GraphImplementation<I,N,D>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Graph<I,N,D>
    The following class represents a graph data structure in which keeps track of its vertices and edges. It implements the interface of Graph. Instead of an adjacency matrix, it is represented with an adjacency list.

    Michael
